description: Product details Zen is to bring harmony to mind and soul. Now you can have a piece of Zen wherever you go at work and at play. The Asus Zenfone 5 Lite A502CG lets you connect record memories and share your thoughts with ease and convenience. Power and maximum connectivity The Zenfone 5 Lite runs on Android 4.4 KitKat offering you a variety of app and customizable choices via Google Play. Download games and use office apps as it packs a powerful Intel Atom Z2520 Chipset that lets you run apps simultaneously. It lets you switch in between apps without freezing or lagging even between high-graphic games. With the laminated TruVivid technology graphics are clearer richer and sharper with 1280 x 720 HD display. Capture random moments in an easy click The Asus Zenfone comes equipped with a powerful 8MP rear camera. Snap a shot of a beautiful panorama or just record your partner’s beautiful smile it lets you record these moments with utmost clarity. Asus’ PixelMaster lets you take professional-quality images using a variety of frunctions from image stabilizer enhanced low light photography noise reduction and breathtaking panoramic shots. Shoot selfies too in utmost clarity. Sounds are better too Asus’ SonicMaster technology offers sublime audio experience that bridges the gap between phone and app software. It lends your low-quality audio from outside sources a boost to enjoy clear bass and clear sound output that SonicMaster can provide. This also provides a better sound to audio mechanics best used for both phone calls and online video calls using Skype and other equivalent apps. Asus is about precision The sleek edges and the seamless metallic design make use of laser precision technology for a premium feel. This laser-point precision is carried with other internal components like the Asus Zentenna. It brings more reliable connections and better receptions even where phone signals are low. This dual antenna lets you enjoy longer continuous phone calls with less signal disruptions and fully utilizes 3G and 4G connections for better mobile internet browsing. Not just built to last it’s also built to last beautiful The wide screen comes with a microscopically-thin coating to fend off smudges stains and fingerprints keeping everything bright for your eye and clean and smooth for your touch while keeping the touchscreen responsive even when wearing gloves. It also comes with a variety of cases and phone accessories you can purchase separately with Lazada’s wide list of Zenfone 5 available and customizable accessories. Additional Information: - 8MP PixelMaster camera: Crystal clear daytime photos vivid night photos & videos up to 400% brighter. - Steady shots with image stabilization. - GloveTouch: Input while wearing gloves - Brand new ASUS ZenUI - Easy to use with intuitive design & multi-color themes

Product details A powerful smartphone need not powerfully punch a hole in your pocket. From one of the country's leaders in the local smartphone industry Cherry Mobile introduces the latest in its ME line - the Cherry Mobile ME Vibe 8GB. Most powerful processor in the market The Cherry Mobile ME Vibe boasts of a powerful octa-core processor that enables the device to seamlessly run multiple task and apps simultaneously. This reduces lags and best for users who are into high-graphic game apps. Shift from your favorite games to Facebook check emails while listening to music the octa-core makes it all possible without lags. It sports of an 8GB internal memory expandable to 32GB for more game and app downloads. Always selfie-ready unlimited apps More than just apps this means more space for selfies and groupies using the 2MP front camera. Take exhilarating panoramas and scenic shots using the 13MP rear camera. Running on Android 4.4 Kitkat and compatible for upgrade to 5.0 Lollipop it gives you unlimited access to more photo editing apps in the Google Play Store. Edit a selfie in Camera 360 and share instantly on Instagram. A touch of ME myself and I Cherry Mobile goes further by letting you accessorize your phone. With the Personalize ME feature you can create back covers that will suit your liking. Choose from a veriety of designs and you can even provide your own images. To make your own personalized back cover: 1. Proceed to the Personalize ME page (http://www.cherrymobile.com.ph/personalize_me) to start. 2. Enter pin code and coupon number found in the scratch card included in the package. 3. Enjoy making your own customized design. Be sure to check on the delivery instructions after the prompt. Whether you're looking for a good smartphone for daily selfies daily Clash of Clans play or simply a reliable device for your travels the Cherry Mobile ME Vibe stands up to the challenge. Help extend your smartphone's battery life by pairing it with a variety of powerbanks available at Lazada.
